{"tid":1983521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(回帶西) 政府第三度抽起大學工程撥款　涉中大港大 2.5 億醫療教學設施撥款","createTime":"2020-04-22T01:30:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T02:18:57.000Z","uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7cda507fc56e57ab05f1e012a7872d6d33851eac","tid":1983521,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T01:30:18.000Z","msg":"政府早前兩度撤回理工大學的工程項目撥款，<span style=\"color: red;\">政府今日再去信財委會，指有議員「表示關注」，因此撤回兩項涉及中大和港大兩項醫療教學設施項目撥款建議，涉及款項約 2.5 億元。</span><br />\n<br />\n兩項撥款已在今年 5 月在工務小組通過，分別是中大在大埔興建一座教學科研綜合大樓，涉及款項 5,970 萬；另一項為港大設施提升及醫學院校區發展的項目，涉及約 1.943 億元，包括興建人體解剖室及遺體存放空間。<br />\n<br />\n財經事務及庫務局向立法會解釋，有議員對財委會文件建議的兩項醫療教學設施工程項目表示關注，「為了讓食物及衞生局有更多時間向議員進行解說，政府決定暫時撤回該撥款建議。」局方稱，會爭取盡快在本立法年度內將有關撥款建議再提交財委會考慮。<br />\n<br />\n政府早前已抽起的理工大學校園擴建工程，同樣與醫療教研設施有關，涉及 14 億元撥款；另外亦指因需檢視工程時間表，抽起擴建理大圖書館的撥款，涉及 3.4 億元。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局回覆《立場新聞》指， 在提升大學的醫療教學設施方面，立法會財委會已於 2018/19 年度通過在基本工程儲備基金整體撥款下向三所大學撥款約 1.8 億元，用作短期的翻新及設施提升工程，局方會繼續積極跟進三所大學其餘的各項中、長期工程項目。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E5%BA%A6%E6%8A%BD%E8%B5%B7%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE-%E6%B6%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7-2-5-%E5%84%84%E9%86%AB%E7%99%82%E6%95%99%E5%AD%B8%E8%A8%AD%E6%96%BD%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%258A%25BD%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%25A8%258B%25E6%2592%25A5%25E6%25AC%25BE-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7-2-5-%25E5%2584%2584%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2599%2582%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E6%2596%25BD%25E6%2592%25A5%25E6%25AC%25BE%2F&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8hD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=c02f98bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%258A%25BD%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%25A8%258B%25E6%2592%25A5%25E6%25AC%25BE-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7-2-5-%25E5%2584%2584%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2599%2582%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E6%2596%25BD%25E6%2592%25A5%25E6%25AC%25BE%2F&h=3a5b7b38\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E5%BA%A6%E6%8A%BD%E8%B5%B7%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE-%E6%B6%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7-2-5-%E5%84%84%E9%86%AB%E7%99%82%E6%95%99%E5%AD%B8%E8%A8%AD%E6%96%BD%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE/</a>"},{"pid":"5b094a9f97bfe11ead6ceab2d526486f10e34eeb","tid":1983521,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T01:32:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee0351ca48c76eaf3ded3ed21cadad801f6cd0e6","tid":1983521,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T01:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c71d730f1b3a2ee7ce6d697760661715f74944","tid":1983521,"uid":293947,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T02:05:33.000Z","msg":"即系香港醫療水平將會繼續下降"},{"pid":"b5d3653dbf1e60f9050fb5cb381b5de771ee1876","tid":1983521,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T02:05:40.000Z","msg":"幫推「資訊戰」 有個痴線佬準備好晒中宣部旗下Youtuber嘅report<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1957525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1957525</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討